  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[but they can have days off during the week]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[and run errands at their leisure]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[while I'm stuck in the office.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[Plus, the state wants me to spend my money,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[and how am I supposed to do that when the shops aren't open when I'm off work?]]></edu>
